column5: hello there,  My friends and I are planning on going to lake scugog tomorrow, where can we dock our boat from around port perry and what kind of fish can be caught out of this lake?  Thank You for your help  - Frank
Bass, walleye, crappie and musky in Scugog. Don't know the Port Perry area but there is a ramp at Caesarea.
there's a dock and ramp in Port Perry... Turn down water st. there will be signs pointing you to the ramp.
